casebody.head_matter:
In re Kelvin SETTLE, petitioner.
No. 13-7738.
Supreme Court of the United States
Jan. 27, 2014.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of mandamus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
